        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(L) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi eterni dei amen. Anno nativitate
                        eius millesimo centesimo septagesimo quarto, decimo kalendas madii,
                        indictione septima. Ex huius cartule pateat recitatione quod nos,
                                <persName><name ref="Tocca">Tocca</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardini</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Monaca">Monaca</name></persName> uxor eius et
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Henrici</name></persName> (…) ubi
                        interfuit notitia <persName><name ref="Bernardus"
                            >Bernardini</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Magaloctus"
                                >Magalotti</name></persName> qui sunt filii nostri (…) atque
                                <persName><name ref="Capitone">Capitone</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Passavanti">Passavanti</name></persName>
                        germani et quondam <persName><name ref="Valle">Vallis</name></persName> (…)
                        necessitate debiti dotis quare dedimus <persName><name ref="Berta"
                                >Berte</name></persName> sorori nostre et pro ipso debito exsolvendo
                        (…) vendimus et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Dominicus"
                                >Dominico</name></persName> converso, accipienti pro <persName><name
                                ref="Montanus">Montanino</name></persName> rectore <rs
                            key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs> seu <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206">Sancti
                            Gilii et sancti Cristofori</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Churches #Hospitals" ref="#places/3207">Altepascio</placeName>,
                        unam nostram terre petiam integram que est posita in loco et finibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/3210" key="#Roads">Putei</placeName> et ubi
                        dicitur <placeName ref="#places/3210">Cafagium</placeName>. Et tenet ambo
                        capita in <rs key="#Roads">viis publicis</rs>, unum latorum tenet in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Crecia">Crece</name></persName> uxoris
                                <persName><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolini</name></persName> et filie
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Lotharius">Lotherii</name></persName>, aliud in
                        terra que olim fuit <persName><name ref="Rusticus"
                            >Rustichelli</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Boncius"
                                >Boncii</name></persName>. Que vero terre petia est per mensuram (…)
                        stariora novem. Et de ipsa terre petia due partes competunt nobis iugalibus
                        et tertia nobis qui supra germani. (…) <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: quatuor
                        centum et viginti quatuor sol. bonorum denariorum Luce vel Pisis factorum.
                        (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum. (…) Leonardus notarius scrivere
                        rogavimus et nos nostrosque heredes obligare placuit. Actum apud <placeName
                            ref="#places/63">Sanctam Mariam ad Montem</placeName> et in loco ubi
                        dicitur <placeName ref="#places/63">ad Colle</placeName>. (…) (S) Preterea
                        suprascripti Tocca et Monaca (…) in pignore dederunt et tradiderunt iamdicto
                        Dominico converso, accipienti pro dicto Montanino rectore iamdicti
                        hospitalis seu ecclesie de Altepascio, duas terrarum petias que sunt posite
                        loco ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/3210">Pratum de Lamis</placeName>.
                        Prima petia terre tenet unum caput in semita, aliud in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Craticus">Craticum</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Arapocus">Arapochi</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Pecora">Pecore</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Fredus">Fredi</name></persName>. Unum latorum tenet in terra
                                <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Hughicio">Uguicionis</name></persName>, aliud
                        in terra Crece uxoris Ugolini et filia quondam Lotherii. Et est (…) stariora
                        tria. Secunda terre petia, que fuit olim <persName><name ref="Raginaldus"
                                >Rainaldi</name></persName>, tenet unum caput cum uno latere in
                        terra predictorum filiorum quondam Vallis, caput aliud tenet in terra quare
                        detinet <persName><name ref="Biloscius">Biloscius</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Signorectus">Signoretti</name></persName>,
                        aliud in terra dicti Martini. Et insuper supradicti Capitone et Passavanti
                        fermani (…) in pignore dederunt et tradiderunt eidem Dominico (…) una terre
                        petiam positam in loco ubi dicitur Pratum de Lamis, et tenet unum caput in
                        terra <persName><name ref="Calabro">Calabronis</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Rogerius">Rogerii</name></persName>, aliud in
                        terra filiorum quondam <persName><name ref="Rondomus"
                            >Rondomi</name></persName>. Unum latorum tenet in terra dicti Tocce,
                        aliud in semita, et est stariora duo. (…) Bernardinus et Magalottus germani
                        predicte venditioni et pingnoris obligationi interfuerunt et dictam eorum
                        matrem interrogaverunt. <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Mainettus"
                                >Mainettus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Bei"
                                >Bei</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Nerus"
                                >Nero</name></persName> magister et quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Hludouuicus">Lodoici</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Wizo">Guittone</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Tuotus">Tuotri</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Guerrus">Guerrus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Iannellus">Iannelli</name></persName>,
                        suprascripti rogati <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs> interfuerunt. (L) Ego
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Leonardus"
                            >Leonardus</name></persName>, domni imperatoris <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs>, post traditam complevi et dedi.</ab>
